column5: Anyone here fishing the Caledonia Walleye derby this coming weekend besides myself and a few buds?
We heard about the derby--what were the rules and times -- results --how can we join in next year -- we fished south of Cayuga on the weekend --no walleye
It's this weekend starting 12 noon 17th. to 19th 12 noon. Got to get your tickets day before the derby at Mikes in Caledonia Boundary below Caledonia dam to above Dunville dam.
